OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FDashcam footage seen at the Nottingham
OL,7,Fattacks public inquiry has been shown
OL,8,Fof a van driven by Valdo Calocane
OL,9,Fhitting two pedestrians amid claims
OL,10,Fthe triple killer was "spooked" by a
OL,11,Fpatrol vehicle.
OL,13,FThe stolen van can be seen failing to
OL,14,Fstop after a police car activated its
OL,15,Fsirens was shown to the inquiry on
OL,16,FFriday, alongside audio of an officer
OL,17,Ftelling his control room "it's running
OL,18,Fpeople over, two people down".
OL,26,@rD@WOUrD@_O]yD@ZOUzD@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
