OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe inquiry has heard how Calocane, a
OL,7,Fformer mechanical engineering student,
OL,8,Ffatally stabbed University of
OL,9,FNottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,10,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,11,F19, on Ilkeston Road, Nottingham, in
OL,12,Fthe early hours of June 13 2023.
OL,14,FHe then went on to kill grandfather
OL,15,FIan Coates, 65, in the Mapperley Park
OL,16,Farea around an hour later, stealing
OL,17,Fhis van and using it to run over
OL,18,Fpedestrians at two locations in
OL,19,FNottingham city centre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FPolice Sergeant Dean Reynolds, who
OL,7,Fspotted Calocane driving the stolen
OL,8,Fvan, and force incident manager, Chief
OL,9,FInspector David Mather, both gave
OL,10,Fevidence to the inquiry about their
OL,11,Frole in responding to the stabbings
OL,12,Fand the vehicle attacks.
OL,14,FSgt Reynolds told the inquiry
OL,15,Fchairwoman that he had taped off part
OL,16,Fof the scene in Ilkeston Road before
OL,17,Fsearching as a single-officer crew for
OL,18,Fa suspect in the "maze" of nearby
OL,19,Fstreets.
OL,26,@zD@ROUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FHe was informed at about 5.22am that a
OL,7,Fpedestrian had been hit by a vehicle
OL,8,Fin Milton Street and offered his
OL,9,Fassistance to attend the incident.
OL,11,FWhile en route through Nottingham city
OL,12,Fcentre, Sgt Reynolds said, he saw a
OL,13,Fwhite van which matched the
OL,14,Fdescription given over the police
OL,15,Fradio and had intended to pull the
OL,16,Fvehicle over, activating his sirens
OL,17,Ffor four seconds.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FSgt Reynolds stopped at the scene to
OL,7,Fhelp the two pedestrians who were hit
OL,8,Fin Upper Parliament Street as Calocane
OL,9,Fdrove off.
OL,11,FSophie Cartwright KC, representing
OL,12,Fsome of the victims who were injured
OL,13,Fby Calocane, asked Sgt Reynolds why he
OL,14,Fwas seeking to pull over a vehicle
OL,15,Fwithout the "approval of command and
OL,16,Fcontrol".
OL,18,FSgt Reynolds answered: "I don't need
OL,19,Fthe approval of command and control to
OL,20,Fpull a vehicle over."
OL,26,@wD@MOUxD@HO]zD@XOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FAs video footage of the events was
OL,7,Fplayed to the court, Ms Cartwright put
OL,8,Fit to Sgt Reynolds: "I am going to
OL,9,Fsuggest to you that this is the very
OL,10,Fpoint where you should have stopped
OL,11,Fand you should have made clear to
OL,12,Fcontrol what the situation was.
OL,14,F"It's the clear recollection of
OL,15,F(victim) Sharon Miller that it was
OL,16,Fyour actions and the pursuit
OL,17,Fimmediately after the audibility of
OL,18,Fthe sirens that she says spooked VC
OL,19,F(Calocane) directly into being driven
OL,20,Fover."
OL,26,@pD@UOUvD@AOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FSgt Reynolds answered that he did not
OL,7,Fbelieve he was pursuing Calocane.
OL,9,FResponding to questions from John
OL,10,FBeggs KC, representing Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice, Sgt Reynolds said it was
OL,12,F"never" his intention to spook
OL,13,FCalocane and had expected him to find
OL,14,Fa safe place to stop and pull in.
OL,16,F"I never thought he would have done
OL,17,Fsuch a thing," Sgt Reynolds said.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@GO]xD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FIn his evidence, Chief Inspector
OL,7,FMather said he had tasked armed
OL,8,Fresponse officers with administering
OL,9,Ffirst aid to Mr Webber and Ms O'Malley-
OL,10,FKumar as a priority, as they had
OL,11,Fbetter medical training than non-armed
OL,12,Fcolleagues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe senior officer, who was the force
OL,7,Fincident manager and also the tactical
OL,8,Ffirearms commander at the time of the
OL,9,Fdouble stabbing, said: "My working
OL,10,Fassumption based on my policing
OL,11,Fexperience was given the location,
OL,12,Fgiven the time of day, given the age
OL,13,Fof the victims... was that this was a
OL,14,Frobbery.
OL,16,F"That was my main hypothesis. Again,
OL,17,Fin my experience, people that commit
OL,18,Frobberies then run away. So my
OL,19,Fexpectation was that the offender's
OL,20,Fintent was to evade capture, so they
OL,21,Fwere fleeing.
OL,26,@qD@XOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773436319
OL,3,CTriple killer 'spooked' by police
OL,4,Csiren on day of Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"I knew that there were two very
OL,7,Fseriously injured individuals at the
OL,8,Fscene.
OL,10,F"And I wanted the ARVs to prioritise `
OL,11,Fusing that extra skill and capability
OL,12,Fthey have ` those two victims and give
OL,13,Fthem every opportunity to survive."
OL,15,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
